WEBVTT

00:00:06.860 --> 00:00:09.940
B.Z. 479'da leşkerê Pers

00:00:09.940 --> 00:00:12.060
bajarê Potidaea dorpêç kiribûn.

00:00:12.066 --> 00:00:14.566
Ava deryayê vekêşiya bû,

00:00:14.660 --> 00:00:17.260
Ew der jî bibû rêya êrişê.

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:19.560
Lê bexte wan reş bû,

00:00:19.576 --> 00:00:21.356
di nîvê rê de,

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:24.960
pêlên avê bi ser wan de hatin,

00:00:24.980 --> 00:00:26.320
hemû xeniqîn.

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:28.880
Gelê Potidaea bawer kirin ku

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:30.700
Poseidon ew rizgar kirine.